{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "萧秋水在峨媚与李沉舟重逢，李沉舟透露自己曾在大渡河观音山江面上远远见过萧秋水，而萧秋水浑然不知。萧秋水追问伏虎寺大侠梁斗被掳之事，李沉舟表示自己昨夜被围于山顶，并非所为。萧秋水将五颗无极先丹交给李沉舟，却引发众人疯狂抢夺。萧秋水当众揭露丹药实为邵流泪所制的剧毒假药，但无人愿听。饶瘦极、九九上人、木归真、储铁诚先后吞服假丹中毒身亡，场面惨烈。五剑叟中鸳鸯剑叟私吞丹药，引发与柔水神君雍希羽的内讧。李沉舟一拳击杀木归真，鸳鸯剑叟临死托言转禀天王恩断义绝后自刎。众人大感索然纷纷退去。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "其实英雄论交，亦不必非要有酒不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "是是是。老弟真合我心意。惟庸人才须杯酒在手，方能作快言豪语，哈哈哈！我筌岂须如此！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我这是第二次见到你，你可知道？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没见过你呀。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "若我见过你，一定认识。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我见到你，你见不到我，因为相隔大远了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你的眼力当不如我好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "是不是……",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "是不是在大渡河与青衣江中……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "原来是你。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "那未伏虎寺中，大侠梁斗等。乃为你所掳了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "什么时候的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "昨晚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "可能。昨夜我己被围于山顶。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "这次我来峨媚，为的是要搜捕那两条蛇干，却不料无端端来了流言，约齐了种种高手，咬定我在此地击杀燕某夺得《忘情天书》，因此困战了整整一天，真是莫名其秒……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "我差点忘了一件事",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "无极先丹？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "我要把它交给你，完成我答允人家的诺言。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "这是屈剑王辛苦抢来的，我当然要收下。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这丹丸原是邵流泪从燕狂徒那儿盗出来的。他把假的丹药，诱使雍希羽将之取去，献给朱大天王，想借刀杀人，可惜屈寒山不知，半途将之夺攫，想奉献给你，所以威迫我这样作……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "那么，这丹丸是有毒的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的，这丹丸含有剧毒！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道这世界上，真话部不如假话能教人相信？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "那也许是因为真话比假话难听之故。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你别自责，说什么也没有用，他们不会听的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "那真的三颗，是让你给吃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "是宋姑娘告诉你的吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "是",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我早知道这药是假的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "你在试探我是不是在骗你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "因为你不曾骗我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "幸亏我不会骗你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "幸亏。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rou_shui_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": "char_yuan_yang_jian_sou",
      "text": "我来断后，快回献天王！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们曾跟我并肩作战过，我不能坐视不理。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他，他吞下去了！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "给他吃了，糟了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rou_shui_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": "char_yuan_yang_jian_sou",
      "text": "你……你竟然私自吞食了？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_jiu_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "九九上人",
      "listener": "char_rao_shou_ji",
      "text": "饶兄你……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_jiu_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "九九上人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……我是不是也一一",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_tie_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "储铁诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是什么药！这是什么丹药！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "铁衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "快拿解药来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_mu_gui_zhen",
      "text": "没有解药。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_mu_gui_zhen",
      "text": "你去吧：",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_tie_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "储铁诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是……这是什么药。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不知道，这药原来是朱大天王的长老邵流泪用来毒死他主子的毒药，现在邵流泪己死，解药也没有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_yang_jian_sou",
      "speaker_name": "鸳鸯剑叟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "为何你…你起先不说？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_yuan_yang_jian_sou",
      "text": "我已经说了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_yang_jian_sou",
      "speaker_name": "鸳鸯剑叟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "替我转禀天王，就说我临死前还对不住他！此刻代他身死，也算恩断义绝了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    }
  ],
